ss=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/igar2k/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7d417cd1e89fdd0f4f19cdb1db74a9f3?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7d417cd1e89fdd0f4f19cdb1db74a9f3?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/igar2k/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Sergio Igartua <small>(igar2k)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 18, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Very easy to set up, very useful to use while building your site. Thanks.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great Plug-in</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cooltattoojonny/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/90a60e880c397ffa2003d145639aec87?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/90a60e880c397ffa2003d145639aec87?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cooltattoojonny/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Jonny Elliot <small>(cooltattoojonny)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 27, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Me Likey</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Semplice e minimale</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/yaku78/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2593f13d383b4d61c976cbf2168f3277?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2593f13d383b4d61c976cbf2168f3277?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/yaku78/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">yaku78</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 13, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Plugin veramente molto semplice e funzionale, non fa molto, quindi se avete bisogno di personalizzazioni dettagliate lasciate perdere, ma quello che deve fare lo fa benissimo. Con un minimo di html+css si possono fare molte cose in pi.\nRiesci 